<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>- وَيَصِحُّ مِمَّنْ يَصِحُّ طَلَاقُهُ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>- وَيَحْرُمُ عَلَيْهِمَا وَطْءٌ وَدَوَاعِيهِ قَبْلَ كَفَّارَتِهِ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَهِيَ:</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c4">[١]</span> عِتْقُ رَقَبَةٍ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c4">[٢]</span> فَإِنْ لَمْ يَجِدْ: فَصِيَامُ شَهْرَيْنِ مُتَتَابِعَيْنِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c4">[٣]</span> فَإِنْ لَمْ يَسْتَطِعْ: فَإِطْعَامُ سِتِّينَ مِسْكِيناً.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَيُكَفِّرُ:</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>- كَافِرٌ بِمَالٍ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>- وَعَبْدٌ بِالصَّوْمِ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>- وَشُرِطَ فِي رَقَبَةِ كَفَّارَةٍ، وَنَذْرِ عِتْقٍ <span class="c2">(١)</span> مُطْلَقٍ:<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c4">[١]</span> إِسْلَامٌ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c4">[٢]</span> وَسَلَامَةٌ مِنْ عَيْبٍ مُضِرٍّ بِالعَمَلِ ضَرَراً بَيِّناً.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>- وَلَا يُجْزِئُ التَّكْفِيرُ إِلَّا بِمَا يُجْزِئُ فِطْرَةً.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَيُجْزِئُ مِنَ البُرِّ:</span> مُدٌّ لِكُلِّ مِسْكِينٍ،<span class="c5"> وَمِنْ غَيْرِهِ:</span> مُدَّانِ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) قوله: (عتق) سقطت من (د).</p> </div>